<plot>Valeria, Claudio and Dino are living in a house on a top of a hill - an old house in a beautiful landscape in Italy. Nobody knows where they were coming from, they just appeared. They seem to be an almost normal family: they observe each other, they quarrel and sometimes they are tender - we watch the little everyday dramas every family might go through. That's what you see and what the film keeps pretending. But something is strange. The 3 protagonists are schizophrenic. Only for the filmmakers they create a formation called family and they play a game called fiction.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?422243</url></doc>
